{"id":408,"date":"2022-07-26T20:14:29","date_gmt":"2022-07-26T20:14:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/?page_id=408"},"modified":"2023-01-10T16:03:56","modified_gmt":"2023-01-10T16:03:56","slug":"privacy-policy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/privacy-policy\/","title":{"rendered":"Privacy Policy"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-left\">Privacy Policy<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Our Commitment To Privacy<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your privacy is important to Digital Silk. In order to better protect your privacy, Digital Silk provides a description of our information practices, including how we collect information, why we collect it, and how it will be used.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What Information Do We Collect?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We collect information submitted through our contact forms and pages. This information must be expressly and voluntarily provided to us \u2013 Digital Silk does not collect it without you knowingly making the decision to give it to us.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the information you may provide includes your name, email address, and phone number. The information is related to projects, services, and billing. Information may also be collected through phone or email conversations via official Digital Silk representatives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, Digital Silk may collect information regarding third parties that is specifically related to you, your project, or the services you requested.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How Do We Use The Information We Collect?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The information that Digital Silk collects is used to provide digital services to you. Some of the ways in which your information could be used by us include, but are not limited, to web support, customer service, project email updates, newsletters, and direct contact in regards to the project and services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk does not share information with outside parties unless it is necessary to complete the services you requested. Digital Silk reserves the right to release applicable information following official judicial practices, such as a valid subpoena or court order.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Do We Use Cookies?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cookies are small files that websites place on individual computer hard drives through web browsers. Users must explicitly allow cookies to be placed by every website that uses them. Cookies enable a website to remember a specific browser, and capture and retain particular information.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk uses cookies to remember, understand and save your preferences for upcoming visits to our website. Cookies help us gather data regarding website traffic, engagement, and interactions, and enable us to provide better future online experiences, tools, and services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The information that our cookies collect has no personal information that can identify you specifically. Conversely, the anonymous information captured by the cookies is transmitted to Google, where it is used to create anonymous web activity reporting only for the domain <a href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\">https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com<\/a>\/. The data is used to gain insight into how to optimize customer experience, content and marketing efforts for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/\">https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, no personally identifiable information will be collected on this website unless explicitly submitted through a fill-in form, such as our Work With Us page.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Remarketing<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk uses cookies to display remarketing advertisements. These are based on a user\u2019s prior visits to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/\">https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/<\/a> and may be seen throughout other websites on the Internet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Users can opt out of cookies through Google at any point by visiting <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/settings\/ads\/onweb\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Google Ads Preferences Manager<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Third-Party Websites<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk\u2019s website may provide links to third-party websites. Digital Silk does not have control over these websites or their content, which have their own unique and independent privacy policies. Thus, we do not assume any responsibility or liability for those websites.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk also does not endorse these websites, including the information and products found on them. If you choose to visit one of the third-party websites linked on this website, it is done at your own discretion and risk.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Digital Silk Is Committed To Data Security<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In order to maintain data security, proper use of information, and information accuracy, Digital Silk has appropriate practices in place to safeguard the information we collect online and offline, including electronic and managerial conduct.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Every online credit card transaction is only performed on secure servers through a secure SSL connection. They also comply with the latest standards in the industry. All billing information, including credit card information, is deleted immediately following the termination or completion of a client project.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Digital Silk Is Committed To Protecting Children\u2019s Privacy Online<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk is committed to protecting children\u2019s privacy. Therefore, we do collect or maintain information at our website from those we actually know are under 13. Our website is also not structured to attract anyone under the age of 13 and is not intended for users under the age of 18.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If we become aware that anyone under the age of 18 has submitted personal information to our website, Digital Silk will delete that information and will not use it for any purpose whatsoever.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk encourages parents and legal guardians to discuss the possible risks of offering personal information through the Internet with their children.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Our Privacy Policy and Your Consent<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>By using our website, you consent to Digital Silk\u2019s privacy policy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If we have any changes to our privacy policy, they will be posted on this web page.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Your Privacy Choices and Rights<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You do not need to provide any personal information in order to enjoy the majority of the features on our website. In addition, you can opt out of certain activities by sending us an opt-out email or by opting out within the activities themselves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Contacting Digital Silk<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions regarding our privacy policy, please contact Digital Silk at:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital Silk<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>16901 Collins Avenue<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Suite 2805<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sunny Isles Beach, FL 33160<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"mailto:info@digitalsilk.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">info@digitalsilk-com<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"tel:8008565417\">(800) 856-5417<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privacy Policy Our Commitment To Privacy Your privacy is important to Digital Silk. In order to better protect your privacy, Digital Silk provides a description of our information practices, including how we collect information, why we collect it, and how it will be used. What Information Do We Collect? We collect information submitted through our&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":96,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"content-type":"","inline_featured_image":false},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v20.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Priv